BuySense AI - Phase-wise Implementation:
Phase 1 (Current Phase) - AI Recommendation Architecture

Goal:
Move from "compare 2 products" to compare every available platform.

What changes?
Create a proper AI module.
Send the entire searched product list to Gemini.
Gemini selects:
   Best Overall
   Best Budget
   Best Rated
   Final Recommendation

After Phase 1 :
User Search
      ↓
search_products()
      ↓
Returns ALL matching products
      ↓
Recommendation Engine
      ↓
Gemini compares ALL platforms
      ↓
Returns recommendation

Components
product_formatter.py

Purpose:
Converts product data into a clean, readable format for Gemini.

Reason:
Language models analyze structured text more effectively than raw Python objects.

ranking.py

Purpose:
Sorts products before AI analysis.

Current Ranking Criteria:

Higher rating first.
Lower price if ratings are equal.


